<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= description %>" />

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon/favicon-32x32.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon/favicon-16x16.png" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/favicon/site.webmanifest" />

    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css" />

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" />

    <!-- Roofle RoofQuote PRO Widget -->
    <script src="https://app.roofle.com/roof-quote-pro-widget.js?id=ZxB2K7X6ylCQKOXoTqCW5" async></script>
  </head>
  <body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header><%- include('partials/header') %></header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-grow">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="relative py-12 md:py-16 text-white overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0">
          <img src="/images/streetview-home.jpg" alt="Roofing Background" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-[center_60%] sm:object-[center_50%] md:object-[center_45%] lg:object-[center_50%]" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-40"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-6 md:mb-0 md:pr-8 text-center md:text-left">
              <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Quality Roofing, Siding & Gutter Services</h1>
              <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-100 mb-5">Protect your home with professional services from the experts you can trust. Serving the local community for over 15 years.</p>

              <!-- Desktop Services Link - Only visible on desktop -->
              <div class="hidden md:block mb-0">
                <a
                  href="/services"
                  class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white hover:bg-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-white transition duration-150 shadow-md"
                >
                  <i class="fas fa-tools mr-2"></i> Explore Our Services
                </a>
              </div>

              <!-- Mobile CTA Button - Shown on small screens -->
              <div class="flex justify-center md:hidden mb-4">
                <button
                  class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg transition duration-300 text-base"
                  onclick="RoofQuotePro.open()"
                >
                  <i class="fas fa-calculator mr-2"></i> Get Your Free Roof Quote
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA Panel - Desktop version -->
            <div class="md:w-1/2">
              <div
                class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4 md:p-5 text-gray-800 relative shadow-[0_10px_50px_-12px_rgba(59,130,246,0.25),0_0_0_1px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] before:absolute before:inset-0 before:rounded-lg before:shadow-[inset_0_1px_2px_rgba(255,255,255,0.9)] before:z-0 after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:right-0 after:h-1 after:bg-gradient-to-r after:from-blue-500 after:to-blue-600 after:rounded-t-lg"
              >
                <div class="relative z-10">
                  <div class="text-center mb-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Get Your Free Roof Quote</h2>
                    <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-sm md:text-base">In Just 60 Seconds</p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2 mb-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                      <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full p-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-green-600 text-xs"></i>
                      </div>
                      <span class="text-sm">No phone call required</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                      <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full p-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-green-600 text-xs"></i>
                      </div>
                      <span class="text-sm">Instant estimate based on satellite imagery</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                      <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full p-1 mr-2 flex-shrink-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-green-600 text-xs"></i>
                      </div>
                      <span class="text-sm">No obligation or pushy sales tactics</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Desktop CTA Button -->
                  <div class="hidden md:block mb-4">
                    <button
                      class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg transition duration-300 text-base relative overflow-hidden group"
                      onclick="RoofQuotePro.open()"
                    >
                      <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700"></span>
                      <span
                        class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 block w-64 h-64 mb-32 mr-4 transition duration-500 origin-bottom-left transform rotate-45 translate-x-24 bg-blue-500 opacity-30 group-hover:rotate-90 ease"
                      ></span>
                      <span class="relative flex items-center"> <i class="fas fa-calculator mr-2"></i> Get Your Free Roof Quote </span>
                    </button>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Trust indicators -->
                  <div class="pt-3 border-t border-gray-200">
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between">
                      <div class="flex items-center space-x-1 text-yellow-400 mb-2 mr-3">
                        <i class="fas fa-star text-sm"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star text-sm"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star text-sm"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star text-sm"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-star text-sm"></i>
                        <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium ml-1 text-sm">4.9/5</span>
                      </div>

                      <div class="flex space-x-2 mb-2">
                        <img src="/images/google.png" alt="Google" class="h-6 w-auto" />
                        <img src="/images/facebook.png" alt="Facebook" class="h-6 w-auto" />
                        <img src="/images/angi.png" alt="Angi" class="h-6 w-auto" />
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 italic">"Received an accurate quote in under a minute. The entire process from quote to finished roof was seamless!" - John D.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Brand Ratings -->
      <section class="py-10 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-2 sm:px-4 lg:px-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl p-2 sm:p-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-2 sm:gap-4 lg:gap-6">
              <!-- Google -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 px-1 sm:p-5 lg:p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center">
                <img src="/images/google.png" alt="Google" class="h-10 sm:h-12 lg:h-14 mb-1 sm:mb-2 lg:mb-3 w-auto" />
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs sm:text-base lg:text-lg">4.7/5</p>
              </div>

              <!-- Facebook -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 px-1 sm:p-5 lg:p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center">
                <img src="/images/facebook.png" alt="Facebook" class="h-10 sm:h-12 lg:h-14 mb-1 sm:mb-2 lg:mb-3 w-auto" />
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs sm:text-base lg:text-lg">4.9/5</p>
              </div>

              <!-- GuildQuality -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 px-1 sm:p-5 lg:p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center">
                <img src="/images/guildquality.png" alt="GuildQuality" class="h-10 sm:h-12 lg:h-14 mb-1 sm:mb-2 lg:mb-3 w-auto" />
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs sm:text-base lg:text-lg">4.8/5</p>
              </div>

              <!-- Yelp -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 px-1 sm:p-5 lg:p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center">
                <img src="/images/yelp.png" alt="Yelp" class="h-10 sm:h-12 lg:h-14 mb-1 sm:mb-2 lg:mb-3 w-auto" />
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs sm:text-base lg:text-lg">4.3/5</p>
              </div>

              <!-- HomeAdvisor -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 px-1 sm:p-5 lg:p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center">
                <img src="/images/home-advisor.png" alt="HomeAdvisor" class="h-10 sm:h-12 lg:h-14 mb-1 sm:mb-2 lg:mb-3 w-auto" />
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs sm:text-base lg:text-lg">4.6/5</p>
              </div>

              <!-- Angi -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2 px-1 sm:p-5 lg:p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center">
                <img src="/images/angi.png" alt="Angi" class="h-10 sm:h-12 lg:h-14 mb-1 sm:mb-2 lg:mb-3 w-auto" />
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs sm:text-base lg:text-lg">4.9/5</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Services Banner -->
      <div class="w-full bg-gray-50 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 sm:py-6 lg:py-10">
          <div
            class="text-center bg-gray-100 py-4 sm:py-6 lg:py-8 px-4 sm:px-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl transform hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 relative overflow-hidden border border-gray-200"
          >
            <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #d1d5db 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 15px 15px"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-6">#1 Premier Siding, Windows, & Roofing Company</h2>

              <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-8 mt-3 sm:mt-6">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full p-1.5 mr-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-600"></i>
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-medium">Financing Available</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full p-1.5 mr-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-600"></i>
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-medium">BBB Accredited(A+ Rated)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full p-1.5 mr-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-600"></i>
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-medium">Locally Owned & Operated</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Services Overview -->
      <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform hover:translate-y-[-8px] transition duration-300">
              <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/roofing-card-image.webp" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Roofing Services" />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Roofing</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Professional installation, repair, and replacement of all types of roofing systems.</p>
                <a
                  href="/roofing"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-blue-600 text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-blue-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition duration-150"
                  >Learn More</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform hover:translate-y-[-8px] transition duration-300">
              <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/siding-card-image.webp" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Siding Services" />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Siding</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Enhance your home's appearance and protection with our quality siding services.</p>
                <a
                  href="/siding"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-blue-600 text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-blue-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition duration-150"
                  >Learn More</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform hover:translate-y-[-8px] transition duration-300">
              <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/gutters-card-image.jpg" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Seamless Gutters" />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Seamless Gutters</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Custom seamless gutters that provide proper water drainage and protect your property.</p>
                <a
                  href="/gutters"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-blue-600 text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-blue-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition duration-150"
                  >Learn More</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform hover:translate-y-[-8px] transition duration-300">
              <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/replacement-card-image.webp" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Replacement Windows" />
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Replacement Windows</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Energy-efficient windows that enhance your home's comfort, appearance, and value.</p>
                <a
                  href="/windows"
                  class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-blue-600 text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-blue-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition duration-150"
                  >Learn More</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Why Choose Us -->
      <section class="py-16 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Choose Us</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">We're committed to quality workmanship and exceptional customer service.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
              <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-medal text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Quality Materials</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">We use only the highest quality materials for all our projects to ensure durability and longevity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
              <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-tools text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Expert Craftsmanship</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">Our team consists of skilled professionals with years of experience in the roofing industry.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
              <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Fully Insured</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">We're fully licensed and insured for your peace of mind and protection throughout the project.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
              <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Satisfaction Guaranteed</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">We're not satisfied until you're completely happy with our work and the final results.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Testimonials -->
      <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What Our Customers Say</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Don't just take our word for it. Here's what our satisfied customers have to say.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
              <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 italic">"Sam's Roofing did an excellent job replacing our roof. The team was professional, efficient, and cleaned up thoroughly after the job was done."</p>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mr-3">
                  <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">John D.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
              <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 italic">
                "We had our siding replaced by Sam's Roofing and couldn't be happier with the results. Our home looks brand new and the price was very reasonable."
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mr-3">
                  <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Sarah M.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
              <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 italic">
                "After a storm damaged our roof, Sam's Roofing came out quickly to assess the damage and make repairs. They even helped with our insurance claim!"
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mr-3">
                  <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Michael T.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
